s&amp;rft.pub=I.B.Tauris&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-85043-764-2&amp;rft.aulast=Lancaster&amp;rft.aufirst=Jordan&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DTnM1g0oKkN0C%26printsec%3Dfrontcover%26dq%3Dhistory%2Bof%2Bnaples%26hl%3Den%26ei%3DM1gjTIm8NcKSOJXu9bkF%26sa%3DX%26oi%3Dbook_result%26ct%3Dresult%26resnum%3D3%26ved%3D0CC4Q6AEwAg%23v%3Donepage%26q%3Dpurgatory%26f%3Dfalse&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAnima+Sola\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cibertol.com/mitos/elanimasola.htm\">\"El Anima Sola\"</a>. Cibertol.com<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">December 20,</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=El+Anima+Sola&amp;rft.pub=Cibertol.com&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cibertol.com%2Fmitos%2Felanimasola.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAnima+Sola\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5000_Spells-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5000_Spells_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Illes, Judika (2004). <i>The Element Encyclopedia of 5000 Spells</i>. London: Element Books. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-00-716465-3\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-00-716465-3\">978-0-00-716465-3</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Element+Encyclopedia+of+5000+Spells&amp;rft.place=London&amp;rft.pub=Element+Books&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-00-716465-3&amp;rft.aulast=Illes&amp;rft.aufirst=Judika&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAnima+Sola\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Perry, Mary Elizabeth; Cruz, Anne J., eds. (1991). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://content.cdlib.org/xtf/view?docId=ft396nb1w0&amp;chunk.id=0&amp;doc.view=print\"><i>Cultural Encounters: The Impact of the Inquisition in Spain and the New World</i></a>. Berkeley: University of California Press. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-520-07098-1\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-520-07098-1\">978-0-520-07098-1</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">December 20,</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Cultural+Encounters%3A+The+Impact+of+the+Inquisition+in+Spain+and+the+New+World&amp;rft.place=Berkeley&amp;rft.pub=University+of+California+Press&amp;rft.date=1991&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-520-07098-1&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcontent.cdlib.org%2Fxtf%2Fview%3FdocId%3Dft396nb1w0%26chunk.id%3D0%26doc.view%3Dprint&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAnima+Sola\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table role=\"presentation\" class=\"noprint navbox metadata plainlist\" style=\"background-color:#f9f9f9;border:1px solid #aaa;clear:both;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-top:0.5em\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:175px\"><span style=\"font-size:125%\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/Portal:Contents/Portals\" title=\"Portal:Contents/